    /** Attaches the Explosion tag from the FireworkStar {@link io.wolfscript.api.inventory.Item}(s)<br> The Explosion Tag is copied from the FireworkStar.<br> Further manipulation on the explosion tag in the FireworkStar will have no effect on the rocket.

{@code true} if successfully removed all FireworkStars; {@code false} if one or more FireworkStars weren't removed /
    public static boolean removeFireworkStars(Item fireworkRocket, Item... fireworkStars) {
        if (fireworkRocket == null || fireworkRocket.getType() != ItemType.FireworkRocket) {
            return false;
        }
        if (!verifyTags(fireworkRocket, "Fireworks", COMPOUND, false)) {
            return false;
